{"tid":1487051,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣疾管署疾病擬人企劃《DISEASE》","createTime":"2019-08-19T05:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:27:49.000Z","uid":44569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"776c72e1ea1a8ecffc8886c41ff32130439e74f3","tid":1487051,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"公家機關的文宣也可以紅到國外。由衛生福利部疾病管制署於 2018 年 11 月起推出的疾病擬人企劃《DISEASE》，不只在國內成功吸引到年輕族群，甚至也受到日本網民的注意，相關文章已被轉推超過 2,000 則。<br />\n<br />\n疾病擬人企劃《DISEASE》早在 2018 年 11 月開始推行，第一位擬人疾病「新型 A 型流感」貼文甫公開就有 1.2 萬以上讚數、4,000 次以上分享。不只人物設定貼近近年的動漫畫風，雜誌文字註解也十分貼近時事。這股風潮有可能是跟著當年轟動一時的《工作細胞》動畫。<br />\n<br />\n而疾管署也在今年初表示會推出 8 種疾病擬人，包含恙蟲病、麻疹、結核病、狂犬病、水痘與帶狀疱疹等。更多樣的人物設定、用色更繽紛，其中讓人聯想到日本偶像團體的「日本腦炎」擬人讓不少日本人都驚呆了&hellip;「台灣真是各方面的不妙（褒）」、「會出畫冊嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfifS62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfifS62.jpg&h=b4f0c9db&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHah6r6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHah6r6.jpg&h=aab15e95&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7dGOFq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7dGOFq.jpg&h=9f35bc2a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xmo0jM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmo0jM4.jpg&h=92004e58&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TdSVkm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TdSVkm.jpg&h=582273a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G90mOFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG90mOFn.jpg&h=7917773c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chGMZM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchGMZM7.jpg&h=a636b53b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoZSaTP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoZSaTP.jpg&h=3248ec23&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Gz6ZNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Gz6ZNa.jpg&h=6cd1aad2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rV2o10x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrV2o10x.jpg&h=1a5b4208&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JM5YQTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJM5YQTJ.jpg&h=72dde9fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFqFjNe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFqFjNe.jpg&h=a52e5b5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf9b0a9bd20a1e9d0e9e867ec4cdbfe8152fec7b","tid":1487051,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"有冇性病=="},{"pid":"9afad8a6ac65d389503b610fd15982485a8634c7","tid":1487051,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e668de9c6722151de2a91d47053efbdfd8c5c6","tid":1487051,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"日本腦炎<br />\npray for kyoani係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b42137eb75b0cca3c65cff151085b8c76f110c8","tid":1487051,"uid":140283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cc8372aee1f8411b96f022f151f2eff67f4393","tid":1487051,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"香港代表港女拜金症候群"}]}